(Republished)

The People of the State of New York, Respondent, v Knovel Everett, Appellant.

— Judgment, Supreme Court, New York County, rendered on October 3, 1977, unanimously affirmed. No opinion. The order of this court entered on May 24, 1979 [70 AD2d 788] is vacated. Concur— Kupferman, J. P., Bloom, Markewich, Yesawich and Ross, JJ.
